Kenya Association of Manufacturers, in partnership with Trademarks East Africa, has launched an online portal to provide investors in the country with up-to-date data.  Present wereÂ  ICT PS Victor Kyalo, Trademark East Africa representative Alban Odhiambo, KAM chairwoman Flora Mutahi with chief executive Phyllis Wakiaga.  The
business portal will provide industry stakeholders and
potential investors with information on economic and legal environment,
industrial and trade statistics relevant to the manufacturing sector and
